                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Anyone want to offer a nice strategy for soloing with a hasted and summoning level 62+ PoP pet? 
<br />

<br />
I seem to get the break at the worst time of course , and once he's damaged you're getting summoned by a 500ish hitting hasted mob.  WoM is what I normally use here of course but I was wondering if anyone had some better suggestions.  One fizzle and one interrupt = dead.
<br />

<br />
Perhaps I just don't have good enough gear to do it reliably as my raid buffed hps are ~4k, ~1600 unbuffed.  I apologize if this is a tangent from the thread;  just popped into my head while reading.
<br />

<br />
