                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is the best AA enchanters get.  It dramatically increases your survivability in just about any crowd control situation and makes charming so much easier.
<br />

<br />
In GoD yesterday it was like the good old days; we had 4-5 adds in camp several different times, sometimes on one pull (LOVE pallys for pulling <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />)and mez mastery let me lock them all down with WoM then Bliss before any of them could tear us up.
<br />

<br />
Absolutely worth the 20 AAs.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=515779" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://lunapark.org/~luna/mithrasig.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
