                                <td colspan="2"><hr /></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Tashim wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=3197&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Pacification</a> is actually less efficient than <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=3359&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Word of Morell</a>, and takes more mana to cast.
<br />

<br />
Personally, the primary reason I got Mez Mastery was to save mana.  Without mez mastery, in order to recharm a pet and get him back into action quickly, I would have to cast </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
I'm not arguing the advantage of Mez Mastery, but look at it like this.
<br />

<br />
On my average normal group, the DPS is such that if we pull 3, they can kill the first and most of the 2nd mob before the 3rd breaks mez.
<br />

<br />
If a pull will grab 6 mobs, then this is what I have in order of casting.
<br />

<br />
WOM       300 mana
<br />
Bliss *5  1500 mana
<br />
Slow *5   500 mana (only use tepid in norms and no point in slowing the almost dead first mob attacked).
<br />

<br />
Sometime during 2nd mob, I'll have to remez (hopefully staggered a bit)
<br />
3 of the 4 mobs.
<br />

<br />
Bliss *3 900 mana
<br />

<br />
Mobs 2, 3, 4 are dead and 5 is underway
<br />

<br />
May or may not have to remez mob 6.
<br />

<br />
Let's say I will
<br />

<br />
Bliss 300
<br />
Reslow mob 6 100.
<br />

<br />
3600 mana for that pull.
<br />

<br />

<br />
My method
<br />

<br />
Pacify *3   1050 mana
<br />
Mez    *2     600 mana
<br />
Slow   *2     200 mana
<br />

<br />
1850 mana.  
<br />

<br />
For the next pull my cost is 800 mana, since Pacify isn't needed.
<br />

<br />
So the total is 2650 mana.  So I've not only saved mana, but the risk to the group is virtually nill.  I love a tough pull as much as the next chanter, but the risk is higher and my mana's going to disapear quickly.
<br />

<br />
As for play style, I prefer to have a charmed pet.  But I also like to have mana.  Although Charm normally lasts at least 1/2 time and often the full length, I've had many times where it breaks several times in a matter of a minute or 2 (my record is 5 times in 2 minutes).  
<br />

<br />
Not sure what my exact mana pool is.  I'm guessing it's over 4 and less than 5k.  Mana regen is VoQ plus FT10 plus MC3</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Without my secret energy pill, I grow weaker and weaker and weaker still.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
